---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Summer School 2026"
  description="Oxford LLMs Summer School 2026 — July 13–17 at Nuffield College."
>
  <div class="container container--content">

    <div class="page-header">
      <p class="section-label">Summer School · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Oxford LLMs 2026</h1>
      <p class="page-header__desc">
        July 13–17, 2026 · Nuffield College, Oxford.<br />
        Full programme and speakers to be announced.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        The 2026 edition of the Oxford LLMs Summer School will continue the programme&apos;s focus on
        large language models for social science, combining lectures, coding sessions, collaborative
        research, and guest talks.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are finalising the detailed programme, speaker list, and collaborative project structure.
        These details will be published here as they are confirmed.
      </p>

      <h2>Dates & Venue</h2>
      <p>
        The summer school will run from <strong>July 13–17, 2026</strong> at
        <a href="https://www.nuffield.ox.ac.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nuffield College</a>,
        University of Oxford.
      </p>

      <h2>Applications</h2>
      <p>
        Information about applications, eligibility, and support will be announced closer to the
        event date.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>

